abstract: Woody Harrelson hosted and Alec Baldwin returned as President Trump. But the Gillis controversy was only hinted at. Maybe.
snippet: Woody Harrelson hosted and Alec Baldwin returned as President Trump. But the Gillis controversy was only hinted at. Maybe.
lead_paragraph: A certain amount of tension always precedes a “Saturday Night Live” season premiere, but this weekend’s curtain raiser, kicking off its 45th year, seemed tenser than usual.

abstract: To the founding fathers, foreign influence on an American president was an abiding fear and a basis for impeachment.
snippet: To the founding fathers, foreign influence on an American president was an abiding fear and a basis for impeachment.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — Alexander Hamilton, as usual, got right to the heart of the matter. When the framers were designing the Constitution and its power of impeachment, one of the high crimes they had in mind was giving into what Hamilton called “the desire in foreign powers to gain an improper ascendant in our councils.”

headline_main: Impeachment Battle to Turn for First Time on a President’s Ties to a Foreign Country

abstract: The party is bracing for a pitched battle with President Trump that will likely overshadow its policy agenda. But Democrats say they do not want impeachment to dominate the election.
snippet: The party is bracing for a pitched battle with President Trump that will likely overshadow its policy agenda. But Democrats say they do not want impeachment to dominate the election.
lead_paragraph: After the 2016 election, Democratic leaders reached an all but unanimous conclusion: To defeat President Trump in 2020, they would have to do more than condemn his offensive behavior and far-right ideology, as Hillary Clinton had done. They would need, above all, to promote a clear and exciting agenda of their own.

abstract: Who knew how much emotion could be invested in a tiny urban garden?
snippet: Who knew how much emotion could be invested in a tiny urban garden?
lead_paragraph: I bought the first tomato plant mostly on a whim. My husband and I had had some casual, preliminary conversations about growing vegetables this summer, but we hadn’t made an official plan when I came home with half a dozen seedlings and no idea what I was doing with them.

headline_main: The Coming Crisis in International Affairs

abstract: In the city where my grandfather was saved, I stood with a young Jewish couple under their wedding canopy.
snippet: In the city where my grandfather was saved, I stood with a young Jewish couple under their wedding canopy.
lead_paragraph: I spend a lot of time in cemeteries. It’s part of the gig: I’m a rabbi. And my Hebrew name — Avraham Yitzhak — is common enough that I often see myself on gravestones, an eerie reminder of the liturgy we’ll recite this Rosh Hashana: “A man’s origin and end is from dust.”

abstract: The killings, many of them against transgender women of color, have deeply disturbed groups already familiar with threats to their safety.
snippet: The killings, many of them against transgender women of color, have deeply disturbed groups already familiar with threats to their safety.
lead_paragraph: ATLANTA — In the most recent killing of a transgender woman, her body was found inside an abandoned car, burned beyond recognition. In another case, the woman was pulled from a lake at a Dallas park. And in a third, she was found dead near a golf course, just weeks after she survived a brutal beating that was captured on video.

abstract: Wary of the former vice president’s slipping poll numbers and the onslaught of attacks from President Trump, some Biden supporters want him to embrace a super PAC.
snippet: Wary of the former vice president’s slipping poll numbers and the onslaught of attacks from President Trump, some Biden supporters want him to embrace a super PAC.
lead_paragraph: Allies of Joseph R. Biden Jr., concerned about his slipping poll numbers in the Democratic presidential primary and an onslaught of attacks from President Trump, are weighing whether to mobilize a super PAC supporting Mr. Biden and have held conversations with wealthy donors to gauge their interest in contributing money.
